 <div class="jumbotron work">
    <div class="container work">
      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
          <h2>A Tradition of Land-based Learning</h2>
          <h4>More than 100 years ago, UC Davis started out as a farm for the University of California.</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3>Leader in the Field</h3>
          <p>Out of that early connection to the land, we’ve grown to be the premier agricultural research institution in the world, and a model within the land-grant university system.</p>
        </div><!--/.photo-->
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3>Sustainable Innovation</h3>
          <p>Now in our second century, we continue to innovate at the frontiers of food and agriculture, and bring a strong focus on sustainability to that work. </p>
        </div><!--/.photo-->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3>Next Generation of Leaders</h3>
          <p>Students from around the world are drawn to work at this interface of Food, Agriculture and Sustainability at UC Davis. Many of these students are part of an innovative undergraduate major in <a href="#">Sustainable Agriculture and Food Systems (SA&amp;FS)</a>.</p>
        </div><!--/.photo-->
  
      </div><!--/.row-->
    </div><!--/.work.container-->
  </div>

